"Commercial License" means a paid license granted by Licensor for production use
outside the Free Use grant in Section 2.

"Production Use" means use of the Software:

(a) in a live environment;
(b) in an internal business environment;
(c) in a customer-facing environment;
(d) in connection with commercial operations, revenue-generating activity, or
the delivery of products or services to third parties; or
(e) in a staging, pre-production, or substantially similar environment that
supports or mirrors any of the foregoing.

Production Use does not include evaluation, development, testing, continuous
integration, security review, local experimentation, or other non-production
activities that do not themselves provide live business or customer-facing
functionality.

"Competing Product" means software, a hosted service, or another commercial
